page.title: 14A DAY OF MY LIFE ALEX
page.content: I get up at 8.00 and wake up everybody else in the house, then I go downstairs and open the curtains and switch on t.v and wait until mum comes downstairs and we have breakfast. After that Oliver and I get dressed and have a cup of tea then we go to school.When we get to school the first thing I do is spellings then handwriting after that we have assembly, then we go outside.When we come in we do maths, then we have dinner at 12.00. When we come in we have reading. And in between we do things like sport,science,computer work,woodwork and sometimes we go on trips for instance Peakirk wildfowl centre. Then we sometimes do singing. At 3.30 we go home. When we get home I watch t.v or sometimes a friend comes round to play
